items.name: Wildcards for Prometheus - camera angles and shots
items.description:
Dr. Derps Prometheus package features a ton of hypernetworks for camera angles and shots, to give you better control of your images. For detailed infos have a look at the model page.

I made those wildcards after a little chat about this package in Discord.

Usage:

Usage is pretty much the same as for "regular" wildcards.

You need the SD Dynamic Prompt Extension. Put the files directly into the wildcard folder:

~\stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-dynamic-prompts\wildcards

They show up as a menu on the left in the Wildcards tab.

The YAML is structured and indented (that's how they work). Just with a little difference. You have to add the category layers in the wildcard.

# choose random weight in 5 suggested strengths (.55,.45,.35,.25,.15)
__dr.derp-hypernetworks/front-shot/full-body__ ${weight=!__weight/*__} 

# chooses set weight
__dr.derp-hypernetworks/front-shot/full-body__ ${weight=.42} 

# you can make it random by adding a wildcard character *
# the example will choose from all angles, but be full body
__dr.derp-hypernetworks/*/full-body__ ${weight=.42} 

# the example will choose from all shots, but be front-shot
__dr.derp-hypernetworks/front-shot/*__ ${weight=.42}

Content

dr.derp-hypernetworks:
    front-shot:
        full-body:
        medium-shot:
        cowboy-shot:
        upper-body-shot:
        close-up-shot:
        extreme-close-up-shot:
    side-shot:
        full-body:
        medium-shot:
        cowboy-shot:
        upper-body-shot:
        close-up-shot:
        extreme-close-up-shot:
    profile-shot:
        full-body:

    back-side-shot:

items.name: Anime-CHIBI4.5
items.description:
This is a way to merge some flat anime models together to achieve a certain CHIBI anime style, which is more flat and cute CHIBI than the common super-detailed anime models.

这是一种将一些平面动漫模型合并在一起，实现某种 CHIBI 动漫风格的方法，与常见的超精细动漫模型相比，CHIBI 更平面、更可爱。

The model is designed to generate CHIBI style images, and the backgrounds generated by the model are also more lovely and flat traced.

该模型旨在生成 CHIBI 风格的图像，由该模型生成的背景也更加可爱和扁平化描边。

It is recommended to use LORA into the model to create even more marvelous results.

推荐使用LORA 到模型中，来创造出更奇妙的结果。

Steps: 40

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras

Upscaler (Hires. fix): R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

Denoising strength: 0.5

Upscale by: 1.5+

CFG scale: 7-13

Recommended Prompt：highres,detailed,best quality,masterpiece,illustration,wallpaper

Recommended Negative prompt：(worst quality, low quality:1.4),nsfw,(hand with more than 5 fingers, hand with less than 4 fingers,ad anatomy, bad hands,mutated hands and fingers:1.2),extra legs,extra arms,interlocked fingers,duplicate,cropped,text,jpeg artifacts,signature,watermark,username,blurry,artist name,trademark,title,muscular,sd character,multiple view,Reference sheet,long body,malformed limbs,multiple breasts,cloned face,malformed,mutated,bad anatomy,disfigured,bad proportions,duplicate,bad feet,artist name,extra limbs,ugly,fused anus,text font ui,missing limb,

This merger is very easy to prompt, but better prompted engineering yields better results.

这种合并非常容易促成，但更好的提示会产生更好的效果。

Note Do not use negative embedding when there is no problem with the image.

注意 当图像没有问题时，请勿使用负嵌入。

Negative pt can be used to fix a variety of distortion issues. It's more likely to affect your original style and can take up a lot of tokens

负pt 可以用来修复各种失真问题。它更有可能影响你的原始风格，而且会占用大量tokens

If you need to use negative embedding, I recommend using verybadimagenegative_v1.3 and badhandv4, and do not recommend easynegative.

如果需要使用负面嵌入，我建议使用 verybadimagenegative_v1.3 和 badhandv4，不建议使用 easynegative。

  • Place the downloaded files into the "embeddings" folder of the SD WebUI
    将下载的文件放入 SD WebUI 的“嵌入”文件夹中

  • In the negative prompt, paste "verybadimagenegative_v1.3, badhandv4"
    在否定提示中，粘贴“verybadimagenegative_v1.3，badhandv4”

items.name: Tooropia - Art Nouveau Darkness
items.description:
This LoRA was based on the work of 19th Century Dutch-Indonesian artist Jan Toorop, who created with a variety of mediums and styles including some atmospheric chalk and pencil drawings which form the training set for this model.

Toorop spent his early years on the island of Java, and later incorporated the elongated figures and lines from Javanese art into his own work.

This model focuses on a dark, moody subset of Toorop's art. Characteristics include a sepia colour scheme, roots and bare tree branches, water, and neoclassical architecture. It presents a contrast to the visually more cheerful Art Nouveau work of artists like Alfons Mucha.

Two versions of this model are available: one trained against the base SD1.5 model, and one trained against a specialised cartoon-style checkpoint. The former will work well with base SD1.5 and photorealistic checkpoints, the latter will work better for Western animation and anime style checkpoints.

items.name: Monica Bellucci (JG)
items.description:
A commission of @Zorglub.

Note: Please also check @sstylerdurden879 fantastic 80s version of Monica.

Monica Bellucci is an acclaimed Italian model and actress. She's best known for her roles in blockbusters such as The Matrix Revolutions or Spectre, among many others.

This is step 120 of a TI trained on a dataset of 15 images with these settings. (I'll probably also upload step 130 later at some point as version 1.0.)

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Building a good prompt with my TIs

You're obviously free to experiment, but bear in mind that my TIs are trained with a more or less fixed phrasing, that normally starts with:

"photo of EMBEDDING_NAME, a woman"

So I recommend always starting your prompt like that and then building the rest of the prompt from there. For instance, "photo of (mbe11ucci:0.99), a woman as a movie star, modelshoot style, (extremely detailed CG unity 8k wallpaper), photo of the most beautiful artwork in the world, professional majestic oil painting by Ed Blinkey, Atey Ghailan, Studio Ghibli, by Jeremy Mann, Greg Manchess, Antonio Moro, trending on ArtStation, trending on CGSociety, Intricate, High Detail, Sharp focus, dramatic, photorealistic painting art by midjourney and greg rutkowski, (white turtleneck top:1.2), ((movie premiere)), (long skirt), ((standing near a movie theater)), ((paparazzi in the background)), (looking at viewer:1.2), (detailed pupils:1.3), ((closeup portrait:1.1))"

items.name: 饮月君 - 飲月君 - Imbibitor Lunae/Honkai: Star Rail - 崩坏：星穹铁道
items.description:
该lora为星穹铁道的饮月君人物，使用anything作为训练底模，并采用了最新的神童优化器，拥有更好的泛化性，测试了几个不同的2d底模都能够完美适应。

在使用该lora的时候需要注意TAG的使用，应当减少对人物优化TAG，过多的TAG会导致人物无法还原(如饮月君的龙角会被一些反向TAG检测为错误的画面而砍掉，为此我独立出一个dragon1\(features\)的TAG用来针对此现象，但在使用的时候仍然需要注意这一点。

不必增加1boy的TAG，因为在训练中我已经将1boy收敛到提示词当中，在你使用1boy的时候会调用底模中的形象，从而影响角色的出图。

以下我使用Counterfeit-V3.0作为参数依据，当然你也可以尝试他来搭配其他的底模。

迭代步数：30

采样方式：DPM++ SDE Karras

宽高：512*768（建议，再通过图生图放大）

提示词参考系数（CFG）：7

lora权重：1-0.6
